{"id": "1288018633070481451", "channel_id": "1288018633070481451", "type": 0, "author_id": "1264288225497714840", "author_name": "kourinn0707_82175", "author_bot": false, "content": "https://youtu.be/6hbOeynp_sg", "timestamp": "2024-09-24T06:06:12.353000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": "2024-09-24T06:08:43.603000+00:00", "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [{"emoji": "🍟", "emoji_id": null, "count": 6}], "attachments": [], "embeds": [{"type": "video", "title": "【忘卻前夜】用13分鐘了解哈姆林的玩法！", "url": "https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=6hbOeynp_sg", "description": "#忘卻前夜  #忘卻前夜攻略\nTOTTOKO 轉圈圈吧 哈姆太郎！\nTOTTOKO 轉圈圈吧 哈姆太郎！\n最喜歡的東西 是向日葵的種子！\n(趕影片中想要加入的咚咚！)\n\n畫面參考：「クトゥルフ神話TRPGシナリオ集「交響曲 『ANIMA』」第一楽章」\n也感謝「愛に奇術師　Cover. LOLUET」陪我趕影片！\n\nBGM：String Quartet No. 2\n\n章節：\n00:00 開場白\n00:13 簡介\n01:11 特殊機制解說\n03:28 技能介紹\n06:29 啟靈介紹&抽取建議\n08:00 玩法說明\n09:21 密契推薦\n11:33 命輪推薦\n12:22 結尾"}], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1288018633070481451", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "哈姆林介紹影片", "forum_channel_id": "1174179624096378930", "thread_tags": ["1283686881858420777"]}
